  }, mdx("pre", {
    parentName: "li"
  }, mdx("code", {
    parentName: "pre"
  }, "Transaction Flat Fee: 1.4% + 10p to 3.4% + 20p\n")), "It\u2019s calculated per transaction and can vary depending on the volume of sales"), mdx("li", {
